{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-post-js",
    "path": "/gitalk-latest-display/",
    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"NARAZUKE","author":[{"name":"nozzle","summary":"who lives in gummaken.","social":{"github":"nozzlex3"}},{"name":"konnyaku","summary":"who is known as Siege Sukosuko Samurai.","social":{"github":"wabetarou"}}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"937ad777-69f5-5014-859f-9a9dbf750aff","excerpt":"仕様 deploy する時に、API で最新のコメントを取得して生成してくれる機能です。 コメントが投稿される度に更新されるわけではないです。 準備 Github GraphQL API 知る GitHub chose GraphQL for our API v4 because it offers…","html":"<h2>仕様</h2>\n<p>deploy する時に、API で最新のコメントを取得して生成してくれる機能です。<br>\nコメントが投稿される度に更新されるわけではないです。</p>\n<h2>準備</h2>\n<h3>Github GraphQL API</h3>\n<h4>知る</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>GitHub chose GraphQL for our API v4 because it offers significantly more flexibility for our integrators. The ability to define precisely the data you want—and only the data you want—is a powerful advantage over the REST API v3 endpoints. GraphQL lets you replace multiple REST requests with a single call to fetch the data you specify.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>引用元：<a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/graphql/overview/about-the-graphql-api#overview\">About the GraphQL API | Github Docs</a></p>\n<p>Github は API の方式を REST から GraphQL に移行した。<br>\nREST API では必要ないデータもまとめて取得する必要がある一方、GraphQL はクライアント側が必要なデータを指定して取得できるため効率的。</p>\n<h4>使ってみる</h4>\n<p><strong>知ってる人は飛ばしてください。</strong><br>\n使ってみるのが一番分かりやすい。<br>\nGraphiQL というグラフィカルなインターフェースを使って API でデータを取得するようすを見てみよう。<br>\n試しに自分のリポジトリとその URL を取得する。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/graphql/overview/explorer\">Explorer | Github Docs</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/56b68/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.88607594936708%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gitalk latest display 01\"\n        title=\"gitalk latest display 01\"\n        src=\"/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/ff44c/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg 158w,\n/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/a6688/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg 315w,\n/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg 630w,\n/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/0ede0/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg 945w,\n/static/4e044907c66eeb8eadf041746af91be6/56b68/gitalk-latest-display-01.jpg 1252w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n<em>explorer の画面</em></p>\n<p>直接クエリを打ち込んでもいいのですが、データの型が分かりやすいし簡単なので explorer を使います。チェックボックスをクリックするたびに、要求するクエリが作られていくので便利です。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>緑色の<code class=\"language-text\">Sign in with Github</code>でログインして Explorer をクリックして数秒待つ。</li>\n<li>Explorer で<code class=\"language-text\">▸user</code>を見つけてクリック。</li>\n<li>紫色の<code class=\"language-text\">login</code>のチェックボックスをクリック。ダブルクォーテーションの間にログイン名を入力。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">▸user</code>下の<code class=\"language-text\">▸repositories</code>を見つけてクリック。</li>\n<li>紫色の<code class=\"language-text\">last</code>のチェックボックスをクリック。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">▸nodes</code>を見つけてクリック。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">name</code>と<code class=\"language-text\">url</code>のチェックボックスを見つけてクリック。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>これでクエリが完成です。\n表示が上のようになってるはずです。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43d7c0241f861bfb923cc788e738d9f2/066f9/gitalk-latest-display-02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 99.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gitalk latest display 02\"\n        title=\"gitalk latest display 02\"\n        src=\"/static/43d7c0241f861bfb923cc788e738d9f2/066f9/gitalk-latest-display-02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/43d7c0241f861bfb923cc788e738d9f2/ff44c/gitalk-latest-display-02.jpg 158w,\n/static/43d7c0241f861bfb923cc788e738d9f2/a6688/gitalk-latest-display-02.jpg 315w,\n/static/43d7c0241f861bfb923cc788e738d9f2/066f9/gitalk-latest-display-02.jpg 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n<em>クエリの表示</em></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>中央上の再生ボタンをクリック。○ の中に ▶ が入ってるボタンです。</li>\n<li>リポジトリ一覧が右に表示されます。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 501px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63444213e8fcf2983f89f17619f81460/305fc/gitalk-latest-display-03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 110.12658227848102%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gitalk latest display 03\"\n        title=\"gitalk latest display 03\"\n        src=\"/static/63444213e8fcf2983f89f17619f81460/305fc/gitalk-latest-display-03.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63444213e8fcf2983f89f17619f81460/ff44c/gitalk-latest-display-03.jpg 158w,\n/static/63444213e8fcf2983f89f17619f81460/a6688/gitalk-latest-display-03.jpg 315w,\n/static/63444213e8fcf2983f89f17619f81460/305fc/gitalk-latest-display-03.jpg 501w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 501px) 100vw, 501px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n<em>応答</em></p>\n<p>確認できたと思います。</p>\n<p>Gitalk ではリポジトリの issue のコメントを使っているので、この API でリポジトリのコメントを取得できるようなクエリを書きましょう。</p>\n<p>自分が書いたものも載せておきます。\nnarazuke.github.io にある最新 100 件の issue にある、最新 1 件のコメントとその日時とユーザー情報を取得します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"query\"><pre class=\"language-query\"><code class=\"language-query\">query {\n    organization(login: &quot;narazuke&quot;) {\n        repository(name: &quot;narazuke.github.io&quot;) {\n            issues(orderBy: {field:UPDATED_AT, direction: DESC}, last: 100) {\n                nodes {\n                    comments(last: 1, orderBy: {field: UPDATED_AT, direction: ASC}) {\n                        totalCount\n                        nodes {\n                            body\n                            author {\n                                avatarUrl(size: 10)\n                                login\n                                url\n                            }\n                            updatedAt\n                        }\n                    }\n                body\n                title\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>gatsby で Github GraphQL API を使えるようにする</h2>\n<h3>access token を取得する</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Github の settings から Developer settings を開く</li>\n<li>Personal access tokens を開いて Generate new token をクリックする。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/9ecec/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.645569620253163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gitalk latest display 04\"\n        title=\"gitalk latest display 04\"\n        src=\"/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/ff44c/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg 158w,\n/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/a6688/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg 315w,\n/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg 630w,\n/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/0ede0/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg 945w,\n/static/82f6da08c88187c737f66c702a1121a4/9ecec/gitalk-latest-display-04.jpg 1050w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>repo だけチェックして Generate token をクリックする。</li>\n<li>token が表示されるのでコピーする。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>plugin を入れる</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-github-api</code>を導入する</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gatsby-source-github-api</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>gatsby-config.js に追記する</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">resolve</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-source-github-api</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">url</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://api.github.com/graphql\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">token</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Developer settingsで取得したトークン<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">variables</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">graphQLQuery</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">query {\n      organization(login: \"narazuke\") {\n        repository(name: \"narazuke.github.io\") {\n          issues(orderBy: {field:UPDATED_AT, direction: DESC}, last: 100) {\n            nodes {\n               comments(last: 1, orderBy: {field: UPDATED_AT, direction: ASC}) {\n                totalCount\n                nodes {\n                  body\n                  author {\n                    avatarUrl(size: 10)\n                    login\n                    url\n                  }\n                  updatedAt\n                }\n              }\n              body\n              title\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>localhost の GraphiQL を確認する</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/7f80b/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gitalk latest display 06\"\n        title=\"gitalk latest display 06\"\n        src=\"/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/ff44c/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg 158w,\n/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/a6688/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg 315w,\n/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/828fb/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg 630w,\n/static/d6e1de884d8db125852fd7dbb5d3dcbb/7f80b/gitalk-latest-display-06.jpg 890w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>githubData と allGithubData の型が出てきたら成功です。あとは graphQL を使ってコメントを表示するプログラムを書きましょう。</p>\n<p>奈良漬で使ってるコードを貼っておきます。<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/narazuke/narazuke.github.io/blob/develop/src/components/latest-comments.js\">https://github.com/narazuke/narazuke.github.io/blob/develop/src/components/latest-comments.js</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/gitalk-latest-display/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gitalkの最新コメントをgatsbyに表示する","created":"2021-02-22T10:59","updated":"2021-02-22T18:20","description":"gatsby-source-github-apiを使います","tag":["gatsby","gitalk","github","graphql"],"author":["nozzle"],"category":"tech"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/noz20210222/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"日記"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/noz20210223/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"日記"}},"relatedPosts":{"totalCount":8,"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-math/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"web 上 で tex の数学記法を使う"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/gitalk-latest-display/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gitalkの最新コメントをgatsbyに表示する"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-embed-link/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gatsbyにyoutube,twitterのリンクを埋め込む"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug"